{"tid":2014663,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼確認《花木蘭》7月北美上畫","createTime":"2020-05-13T07:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T06:16:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"050701f1400c791b700d29e4c691cedfc3f327da","tid":2014663,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:17:09.000Z","msg":"因為武漢肺炎（COVID-19，新冠肺炎）關係造成電影延後上映的迪士尼真人動畫電影《花木蘭》，4月初宣布將在7月24日於北美上映，近日迪士尼CEO鮑伯查佩克（Bob Chapek）接受媒體採訪時，也再度談到此消息，表示會遵守原先的時間正常上映。<br />\n<br />\n鮑伯查佩克上任之後次接受「CNBC」採訪時透露，對於疫情舒緩相當有信心，也談到旗下新作的動向：「對於《花木蘭》能夠準時在各地上映保持樂觀態度，我也認為民眾因為疫情關係，想看電影的心情一定累積已久，《花木蘭》安排在7月底上映，我認為是很好的檔期，屆時期待會有亮眼成績。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/02/1997842-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F02%2F1997842-XXL.jpg&h=70fd9e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上除了《花木蘭》之外，迪士尼另一部受注目的作品《黑寡婦》也拍板會在11月6日於北美上映，而在這之前，還有華納兄弟出品，由克里斯多福諾蘭執導的《天能》當前鋒，預計會在7月17日上映，屆時會面臨何種挑戰，也讓人相當好奇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/E/news.aspx?newsid=741528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FE%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D741528&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=841086f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FE%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D741528&h=09c0576a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/E/news.aspx?newsid=741528</a>"},{"pid":"8e7f8cd9bf025d252fc38fb0c46e1f349084f43b","tid":2014663,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:40:08.000Z","msg":"狗先睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4da5e80460627a65716b62f78794d13646efbb3","tid":2014663,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:42:12.000Z","msg":"我係美籍中國人<br />\n我要睇了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3421dce155418fe911605e0083d79358d2e36993